⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Gen. Thomas Purcell
node COR · COR · ⟦Gen. Thomas Purcell:COR:509720⟧

WHO   — Gen. Thomas Purcell — the hand behind DESTINI
WHAT  — The dark-hubris figure: the man whose technology caused the crisis, who would deploy the same flawed weapon again rather than admit what it did.
WHERE — COR · The Core  Framework inputs: The Core (2003, dir. Jon Amiel)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the film's true villain isn't nature but a power that wields what it can't understand and protects itself before the planet.
HOW   — By rank, secrecy, and the will to reach again for DESTINI — the broken tool that broke the world.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I built a thing I didn't understand and aimed it at the Earth — and my first instinct was to fire it again.

